# Cluster Information Pane Structure

The cluster information view is implemented under `src/cluster/components/`.

- **Main Component:** [`ClusterInfoPane.tsx`](mdc:src/cluster/components/ClusterInfoPane.tsx) orchestrates the layout.
- **Layout:** Uses [`react-resizable-panels`](mdc:https:/github.com/bvaughn/react-resizable-panels) to create a three-pane layout (Sidebar, List, Detail). This library is also used in [`MainLayout.tsx`](mdc:src/main/MainLayout.tsx).
- **Sidebar:** [`ResourceKindSidebar.tsx`](mdc:src/cluster/components/ResourceKindSidebar.tsx) displays Kubernetes resource kinds grouped by API category in an accordion style.
- **Resource List:** [`ResourceList.tsx`](mdc:src/cluster/components/ResourceList.tsx) shows a list of resources for the selected kind.
- **Detail Pane:** [`ResourceDetailPane.tsx`](mdc:src/cluster/components/ResourceDetailPane.tsx) displays details for a selected resource.
- **Styling:** Component-specific styles are defined in [`ClusterInfoPane.css`](mdc:src/cluster/components/ClusterInfoPane.css) using global CSS with kebab-case class names.
